F / H / G — squad: follow / hold / attack-move
Mouse Wheel  or  + / −  — zoom      R — restart battle      Esc — pause / quit to menu
Couch Co-op:  P1 = keyboard + mouse      P2 = gamepad (left stick move, right stick aim)"
